  This article describes several &lt;b&gt;text-level/b&gt; elements. It explains their usage in an &lt;b&gt;HTML&lt;/b&gt; document.   
&lt;/p&gt;
Keywords are displayed with the default style of the &lt;b&gt; element, likely in bold.

