  &lt;dd&gt;A free, open source, cross-platform, graphical web browser
      developed by the Mozilla Corporation and hundreds of volunteers.&lt;/dd&gt;

  &lt;!-- other terms and definitions --&gt;
&lt;/dl&gt;

